China Plans Qian River Hydropower Dam in Guangxi Region, Government Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-03-18T09:00:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/china-plans-qian-river-hydropower-dam-in-guangxi-region-government-says.html
China plans to build a hydropower
dam downstream of Qian River in the region of Guangxi, with
designed installed capacity of 1.6 million kilowatts, the
National Development and Reform Commission said today.  The investment of the project is about 28 billion yuan
based on an estimate in 2009, the commission said in a statement
posted on its website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  